Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.39,1:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她脱光了吗?  看不出来\N{\rEng}ls she naked?  You can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.90,1:09:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对准\N{\rEng}Get it focused.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.37,1:09:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了 等轮到你再说\N{\rEng}Will you stop? Wait your turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.90,1:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are they doing?
