Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.36,1:09:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 她在他上面\N{\rEng}Hold on. She's on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.71,1:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的手插在她头发里\N{\rEng}He's rubbing his hands through her hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.58,1:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看  不 这是我的望远镜 瑞斯\N{\rEng}Let me look.  No. No, it's my telescope, Chase.
