Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.73,1:09:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男人穿着汉堡屋的制服\N{\rEng}That man's in a burger chalet uniform.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.39,1:09:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看\N{\rEng}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.83,1:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊谁知道下一个有艳遇的是谁\N{\rEng}Yeah. You never think that those guys ever get lucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.70,1:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着她问我 刚才的事算不算下流\N{\rEng}Then she asks me if what we'd just done was dirty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.30,1:09:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道该怎么说 我说不是\N{\rEng}l knew what to say. l said no.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.84,1:09:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着她拉着我的手问"你喜欢我 是吗?"\N{\rEng}Then she goes, ''You like me, don't you?''
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.84,1:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没说 最好让小妞们猜测\N{\rEng}l didn't say anything. lt's best to keep chicks guessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.78,1:10:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞斯 宝贝儿 晚饭前得练习小提琴\N{\rEng}Chase, honey. Come practice your violin before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.12,1:10:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会相信的\N{\rEng}You're not going to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.70,1:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勒克斯今晚又上屋顶了!\N{\rEng}Lux is on the roof again tonight!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.79,1:10:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的手在下滑 我得看看\N{\rEng}Her hands are moving down. l gotta see this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.39,1:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太美了  现在是她在上面了\N{\rEng}This is beautiful.  Now she's on top of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.86,1:10:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在做什么 伙计?  等等\N{\rEng}What's she doing, man?  Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.40,1:10:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在做完了 他起来了\N{\rEng}Now they're done. He's getting up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.27,1:10:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样? 真是快\N{\rEng}That's it? That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.78,1:10:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...再加1 如果指数是时间\N{\rEng}...plus one. And if the exponential is time
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.98,1:10:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就有…\N{\rEng}then you'd have as you approach...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.76,1:10:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安\N{\rEng}Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.11,1:11:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用光合作用做早餐了吗?\N{\rEng}Have we photosynthesized our breakfast today?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.14,1:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 罗纳德 嗨 哈里\N{\rEng}Hello, Ronald. Hi, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.78,1:11:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的女儿们已经两周没来上学了\N{\rEng}Your daughters haven't been at school for over two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.22,1:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你查过了?\N{\rEng}Have you checked out back?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.26,1:11:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们找了个新数学老师\N{\rEng}They've found a new Math teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.73,1:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他得找新工作了 我知道\N{\rEng}He'll have to get another job. l know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.60,1:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩们还要这样被关多久?\N{\rEng}How long can those girls be cooped up like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.62,1:11:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开 这是我们的树\N{\rEng}Go away. This is our tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.49,1:11:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩们 女孩们…为时已晚 这棵树已经死了\N{\rEng}Girls, girls... lt's a little late. This tree is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.63,1:11:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让它自生自灭呢?\N{\rEng}Why don't you leave it up to Nature?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.34,1:11:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样所有树都会死\N{\rEng}lf we did, there'd be no trees left.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.33,1:12:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正最后结果也一样\N{\rEng}That's what it's going to be like anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.17,1:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真菌没从欧洲扩散\N{\rEng}lf they didn't bring the fungus from Europe
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.66,1:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不会这样了\N{\rEng}this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.77,1:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 走吧\N{\rEng}OK. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.91,1:12:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不走?\N{\rEng}No?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.44,1:12:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样 我收到命令要砍掉你们的榆树\N{\rEng}That's it. l have an order to cut down your elm tree,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.75,1:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的孩子们不让\N{\rEng}but your kids won't let us.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.22,1:12:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道树有病\N{\rEng}How do you know it's sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.63,1:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 它叶子都黄了\N{\rEng}Believe me or not, it has yellow leaves,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.87,1:12:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的死了 it’s dead for Christsake.\N{\rEng}Are you familiar with arbotect?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.11,1:12:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道毒疗法吗\N{\rEng}Our daughter show us an article
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.55,1:12:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿给我看的文章\N{\rEng}says it was less aggressive therapy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.83,1:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里说这创伤较小\N{\rEng}lt doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.96,1:12:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用\N{\rEng}l leave that tree there, they'll all go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.66,1:12:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是把它留着 明年所有树都会死
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.14,1:12:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早晚都会死嘛\N{\rEng}They could anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.63,1:12:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我不想打电话给警察\N{\rEng}Look, l don't want to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.00,1:12:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿站在自家草坪上\N{\rEng}Our daughters are standing on our lawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.55,1:12:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这犯哪门子的罪?\N{\rEng}Since when is that a crime?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.95,1:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里弗 看到那些穿睡衣的女孩了吗?\N{\rEng}Clive. See those girls in their nighties?
