Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.71,1:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想拍穿睡衣的女孩\N{\rEng}l want those girls in their nighties.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.63,1:13:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面一点 放松点\N{\rEng}Let's back up. Give me some more slack.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.90,1:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这样行吗? 好\N{\rEng}There you go.ls that good? Great.
