Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.66,1:14:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是人间尤物\N{\rEng}You're the stone fox.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.16,1:14:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩们与世界的唯一联系\N{\rEng}The girls' only contact with the outside world
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.66,1:14:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她们订的杂志\N{\rEng}was through the catalogues they ordered.
