Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.75,1:15:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扫满地青苔的日本老人\N{\rEng}tidying a moss carpeted speck of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.57,1:15:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们订了同样的杂志\N{\rEng}We ordered the same catalogues
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.46,1:15:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与她们在蒙尘的小道上远足\N{\rEng}and hiked through dusty passes with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.61,1:15:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时不时停下\N{\rEng}Stopping every now and then
