Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.60,1:15:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将手放在她们温暖 湿润的肩膀上\N{\rEng}Placing our hands on their warm, moist shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.84,1:15:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共赏日落的余辉\N{\rEng}and gazing off at the fire sunsets.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.84,1:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们和她们一起在凉亭喝茶\N{\rEng}We drank tea with them in a water pavilion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.78,1:15:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们随心所欲\N{\rEng}We did whatever we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.25,1:15:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞西利亚没有死 她是加尔各答的新娘\N{\rEng}Cecilia hadn't died. She was a bride in Calcutta.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.12,1:15:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法实现的旅行\N{\rEng}The only way we felt close to the girls
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.69,1:15:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们走近她们的唯一方法\N{\rEng}was through these impossible excursions
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.40,1:15:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让我们铭记终生\N{\rEng}which have scared us forever,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.93,1:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些梦比真实的女人更让我们快乐\N{\rEng}making us happier with dreams than wives.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.40,1:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们收集她们所有的东西\N{\rEng}Collecting everything we could of theirs,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.33,1:16:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩们萦绕在我们脑海里\N{\rEng}the Lisbon girls wouldn't leave our minds,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.58,1:16:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她们在消逝\N{\rEng}but they were slipping away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.08,1:16:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们眼睛的颜色渐渐淡去\N{\rEng}The colors of their eyes faded along
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.11,1:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连同消失的酒窝\N{\rEng}with the exact location of their dimples.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.28,1:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五个变成了四个\N{\rEng}From five they had become four,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.14,1:16:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如行尸走肉般活着…\N{\rEng}and they were all living in the dead...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.42,1:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成了影子\N{\rEng}becoming shadows.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.96,1:16:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她们没有联系我们\N{\rEng}We were losing them
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.18,1:16:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就彻底失去她们了\N{\rEng}when the girls contacted us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.43,1:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1长 2短\N{\rEng}One long. Two short.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.40,1:16:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1长 记下了?\N{\rEng}One long. Have you got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.57,1:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 好的\N{\rEng}That's it. OK.
