Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.38,1:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送来\N{\rEng}Send.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.61,1:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bo... Bo.\N{\rEng}Bo... Bo Bo... Bo.
